SELECT ->
  select distinct FIELD_LIST
  | select FIELD_LIST

  FIELD_LIST , FIELD

FROM ->
  from id

WHERE ->
  where EXPR

LIMIT ->

  | fetch first number rows only
  | fetch first number row only

GROUP_BY ->
  group by ID_LIST

ID_LIST ->
  id
  | ID_LIST , id

HAVING ->
  having EXPR

ORDER_BY ->
  order by id asc
  | order by id desc
